<br>
There was a 5th spell added to each line, so the level 44 (4th)battle shout did not get changed.<br>
<br>
The progression of the spell lines were extended. The code and formula's written to the 4th spell in each line was already implemented and tested. If you change any of this it would create a lot more work. More work means things get pushed back. <br>
<br>
Thanks for the explaination Mackey. It makes a lot more sense now. <p>Padar, 50 Kobold Skald Palomides<br>
