Evade I and dodger II: 5% + 2 *  3 % = 11% evade base chance (before attributes)<br>
<br>
Evade II (hunter) : 10% evade base chance (before attribute bonus)<br>
<br>
The last time I checked my maths book 11% was more that 10%.... <br>
